'''Markos Giolias''' ({{lang-el|Μάρκος Γκιόλιας}}) is a historian and writer.<ref>{{cite news|last=Papayiannides|first=Mary|title= Τα Βιβλία σε  RSS Τοπική ιστορία|url=http://www.tovima.gr/default.asp?pid=2&ct=47&artid=116637&dt=21/11/1999|accessdate=11 November 2010|newspaper=TO BHMA|date=12 November 1999|language=Greek}}</ref> He was born in [[Granitsa, Evrytania|Granitsa]], Evrytania and is a professor at [[Panteios University]].

